###########################################################################
#  eq_matrix_4x4 - a 4x4 bracketed matrix, deeper than eq_matrix_3x3,
#  with mixed numeric / variable / scripted entries. Forces the matrix
#  layout machinery to balance four columns of unequal natural widths.
###########################################################################

@SysInclude { eq }
@SysInclude { doc }
@Doc @Text @Begin
@PP
A 4x4 identity-shaped matrix with scripted off-diagonals:
@DP
@CentredDisplay @Eq { A = left [ matrix
   above { acol { 1 } { a sub 21 } { a sub 31 } { a sub 41 } }
   above { acol { a sub 12 } { 1 } { a sub 32 } { a sub 42 } }
   above { acol { a sub 13 } { a sub 23 } { 1 } { a sub 43 } }
   above { acol { a sub 14 } { a sub 24 } { a sub 34 } { 1 } }
] right ] }
@End @Text
